<title>&quot;THE LORD IS KING&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kum khawtuong la chuh ngaiun,
 Vana hung gi chuh;
 &quot;Lopi, lopina um hen,
 Pathien kawmah!&quot;
 Gamvak nuomtak apatin,
 Angel leh mithiengte'n la sa'n;
 Kingkang tuma lahawih sa'n,
 &quot;Lalpen!&quot; tiin.

[V2]
 2. Zawhna lahawih chu ngaiun,
 Khawvel gam thawng chuh;
 Tuisuohgiet luonggi bangin,
 Kipah la gi;
 &quot;Hallelujah! Lal pakchau!&quot;
 Gamtin chenga zawhna la sa'n;
 Aw gi ngeih leh hawih takin,
 &quot;Lalpen!&quot; tiin.

[V3]
 3. Thum khat-a um a pak ui,
 Vana mipi te'n;
 Pa, Chapa, Thagau thiengtho,
 A chawian ui;
 Hun chiehsa a mah bangin,
 Kumsawt in zie la hi gina;
 Tatsate'n phuong zing unau,
 &quot;Lalpen&quot; tiin.</lyrics>
</song>